<li id="cite_note-7"><span class="mw-cite-backlink"><b><a href="#cite_ref-7">^</a></b></span> <span class="reference-text"><link rel="mw-deduplicated-inline-style" href="mw-data:TemplateStyles:r1133582631"><cite id="CITEREFKoren2018" class="citation news cs1">Koren, Marina (October 24, 2018). <a rel="nofollow" class="external text" href="https://www.theatlantic.com/science/archive/2018/10/lawrence-krauss-sexual-misconduct-me-too-arizona-state/573844/">"Lawrence Krauss and the Legacy of Harassment in Science"</a>. <i><a href="/wiki/The_Atlantic" title="The Atlantic">The Atlantic</a></i>. <a rel="nofollow" class="external text" href="https://web.archive.org/web/20210530042235/https://www.theatlantic.com/science/archive/2018/10/lawrence-krauss-sexual-misconduct-me-too-arizona-state/573844/">Archived</a> from the original on May 30, 2021<span class="reference-accessdate">. Retrieved <span class="nowrap">May 14,</span> 2021</span>.</cite><span title="ctx_ver=Z39.88-2004&amp;rft_val_fmt=info%3Aofi%2Ffmt%3Akev%3Amtx%3Ajournal&amp;rft.genre=article&amp;rft.jtitle=The+Atlantic&amp;rft.atitle=Lawrence+Krauss+and+the+Legacy+of+Harassment+in+Science&amp;rft.date=2018-10-24&amp;rft.aulast=Koren&amp;rft.aufirst=Marina&amp;rft_id=https%3A%2F%2Fwww.theatlantic.com%2Fscience%2Farchive%2F2018%2F10%2Flawrence-krauss-sexual-misconduct-me-too-arizona-state%2F573844%2F&amp;rfr_id=info%3Asid%2Fen.wikipedia.org%3ASurely+You%27re+Joking%2C+Mr.+Feynman%21" class="Z3988"></span></span>
